            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Well, there are a lot of drugs that can cause a heart attack in large doses.  For example. potassium chloride or dioxides... But... we won't be able to tell without doing an autopsy.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 好了，在現場發現了好多藥，大劑量的用藥導致了心臟病發。比如，鉀氧化物或二氧化碳⋯⋯ 但⋯⋯ 在驗屍前這些我們都無從得知。
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Damn!
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 該死！
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Snake, I want you and Meryl to work together!
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | Snake，我希望你和Meryl一起協作。
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Can I trust her?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 她可靠嗎？
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | ...More than you can trust me.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 比我可靠。
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | ......
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | ⋯⋯
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Get in contact with her.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 跟她聯繫。
        .dialog
            em.name.name-mei-ling
                | Mei Ling
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Snake, there is a lot of electrical interferance coming from there. It should be okay if you do burst transmission like us but normal transmission is probably impossible.  Try moving away from that area.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | Snake，你那裏有好多電子干擾。現在你沒辦法像平常一樣給我們發電波，請離開這塊地方。
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Snake, get a hold of yourself.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | Snake，控制下你的情緒。
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Naomi, what the hell was that ninja thing?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | Naomi，那個忍者是個什麼鬼情況？
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | .....
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | ⋯⋯
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | A member of FOX-HOUND?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | FOX-HOUND的成員？
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | No...
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 不⋯⋯
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Are you sure?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 你確定？
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Yes, we have no one like that in our unit.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 是的，FOX-HOUND裏沒有他。
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Is that right?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 真的？
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Snake, I'm counting on you. (The transmission ends and Snake is left to find Meryl's Codec frequency.  He does find it on the back of the CD case and contacts her.)
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | Snake，就靠你了。（這次通話結束後，Snake找到了Meryl的電波頻率.）
