    .section
        audio(src="./assets/audio/cd1/vox/100069_Just_what_I'd_expect_from_the_legendary_Solid_Snake.mp3", controls="")
        .dialog
            em.name.name-meryl
                | Meryl
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Just what I'd expect from the legendary Solid Snake.  You trying to sweep me off my feet?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 我沒料到傳奇的Solid Snake會說出這樣的話，那你有沒掃視我的雙腳？
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Don't worry.  You'll land back on them once you meet me.  The reality is no match for the legend, I'm afraid.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 別擔心，妳返回的時候，我還以為是最後一次見妳了，現實不是傳說，我很擔心你。
        .dialog
            em.name.name-meryl
                | Meryl
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | I don't believe that.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 我真不敢相信。
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Why did you look surprised when you saw my face?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 為什麼你在看到我的時候一臉詫異？
        .dialog
            em.name.name-meryl
                | Meryl
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Because you look just like him.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 因為你看起來像他。
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | ...You mean the terrorists leader, Liquid Snake?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 你想說恐怖份子首領，Liquid Snake？
        .dialog
            em.name.name-meryl
                | Meryl
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Yeah, you know him?  You're not brothers are you!?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 對啊，你知道他？你不是他兄弟嗎？
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | I have no family.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 我沒有家人。
        .dialog
            em.name.name-meryl
                | Meryl
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | So, what's the deal then?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 那是怎麼回事？
